@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
actor "Admin" as A
control "User" as U
actor "Moderator" as M
control "Advertiser" as A2
M -> A : Like Post
activate A
A --> M : ACK
deactivate A
note over A : processing like post
M ->> A : Send Message
A -> A2 : Comment
note over A2 : processing comment
A -> M : Edit Profile
A2 -> A : Create Post
@enduml